@startuml Booking Lifecycle Sequence Diagram

title Staff Booking Lifecycle & GPS Tracking

actor Staff
actor Renter
participant "Frontend\n(Staff)" as FE
participant "Frontend\n(Renter)" as FER
participant "Backend\nStaffBookingController" as API
participant "BookingServiceImpl" as SVC
participant "PaymentTransactionService" as PTS
participant "PayOS" as PAYOS
participant "Database" as DB

== Step 1: Staff Views Booking Details ==

Staff -> FE: Navigate to /staff/bookings
FE -> API: GET /api/staff/bookings?page=0&size=10
API -> SVC: getAllBookings(spec, pageable)
SVC -> DB: findAll(spec, pageable)
DB --> SVC: Page<Booking>
SVC --> API: Page<AdminBookingResponse>
API --> FE: 200 OK (paginated bookings)
FE --> Staff: Display booking table

Staff -> FE: Click "View" on a booking
FE -> API: GET /api/staff/bookings/{bookingId}
API -> SVC: getAdminBookingById(bookingId)
SVC -> DB: findById(bookingId)
DB --> SVC: Booking (status=CONFIRMED)
SVC --> API: AdminBookingResponse
API --> FE: 200 OK (booking detail)
FE --> Staff: Display Booking Detail Page\n(info, cars, prices, payments, actions)

== Step 2: Staff Confirms Car Pickup (CONFIRMED → IN_PROGRESS) ==

Staff -> FE: Click "Confirm Pickup"
FE -> API: PUT /api/staff/bookings/{bookingId}/confirm-pickup
API -> SVC: confirmPickup(bookingId)
SVC -> DB: findById(bookingId)
DB --> SVC: Booking (status=CONFIRMED)
SVC -> SVC: Validate status == CONFIRMED
SVC -> SVC: Set actualReceiveDate = now()
SVC -> SVC: Set status = IN_PROGRESS
SVC -> DB: save(booking)
DB --> SVC: Updated Booking
SVC --> API: AdminBookingResponse
API --> FE: 200 OK (booking with IN_PROGRESS)
FE --> Staff: Show success toast\n+ GPS Tracking section appears

== Step 3: GPS Tracking (Emulated) — During IN_PROGRESS ==

note over FE
  **Client-side only emulation**
  No backend calls for GPS.
  Leaflet.js + OpenStreetMap tiles.
end note

FE -> FE: Initialize GPS emulation\n(setInterval every 3s)
FE -> FE: Generate random lat/lng offsets\nfrom HCMC center (10.7769, 106.7009)
FE -> FE: Update car markers on map
FE -> FE: Draw route polyline (trail)
FE -> FE: Show speed (20-80 km/h),\ndistance, elapsed time
FE --> Staff: Live map with car movement

== Step 4: Staff Confirms Car Return ==

Staff -> FE: Click "Confirm Return"
FE -> API: PUT /api/staff/bookings/{bookingId}/confirm-return
API -> SVC: confirmReturn(bookingId)
SVC -> DB: findById(bookingId)
DB --> SVC: Booking (status=IN_PROGRESS)
SVC -> SVC: Validate status == IN_PROGRESS
SVC -> SVC: Set actualReturnDate = now()
SVC -> SVC: Compare actualReturnDate\nvs expectedReturnDate

alt No Overdue (on time or early)
    SVC -> SVC: Set status = COMPLETED
    SVC -> DB: save(booking)
    DB --> SVC: Updated Booking
    SVC --> API: AdminBookingResponse (COMPLETED)
    API --> FE: 200 OK
    FE --> Staff: Show "Booking Complete" banner

else Has Overdue (late return)
    == Step 5: Overdue Charge Calculation ==

    SVC -> SVC: overdueHours = ceil(\n  actualReturnDate - expectedReturnDate)
    SVC -> DB: Fetch cars → get hourly rate
    DB --> SVC: Cars with CarType.price
    SVC -> SVC: overdueCharge =\n  overdueHours × hourlyRate × carCount × 1.5
    SVC -> SVC: Update booking:\n  totalPrice += overdueCharge\n  remainingAmount += overdueCharge\n  overdueCharge = overdueCharge

    == Step 6: Create Overdue Payment ==

    SVC -> PTS: createPayment(bookingId,\n  OVERDUE_PAYMENT, overdueCharge)
    PTS -> PAYOS: createPaymentLink(\n  orderCode, amount, bookingId)
    PAYOS --> PTS: checkoutUrl
    PTS -> DB: save(PaymentTransaction\n  purpose=OVERDUE_PAYMENT,\n  status=PENDING)
    DB --> PTS: Saved transaction
    PTS --> SVC: PaymentTransactionResponse\n  (with paymentUrl)

    SVC -> SVC: Keep status = IN_PROGRESS\n(awaiting overdue payment)
    SVC -> DB: save(booking)
    DB --> SVC: Updated Booking
    SVC --> API: AdminBookingResponse\n(with overdueCharge + payment)
    API --> FE: 200 OK
    FE --> Staff: Show Overdue Alert banner\n+ OVERDUE_PAYMENT (PENDING)\nin payment history

    == Step 6b: Renter Pays Overdue Fees ==

    Renter -> FER: View booking details
    FER --> Renter: Show overdue charge\n+ "Pay Now" button
    Renter -> FER: Click "Pay Now"
    FER -> PAYOS: Redirect to PayOS checkout
    Renter -> PAYOS: Complete payment
    PAYOS -> API: Webhook (orderCode, PAID)
    API -> API: handleWebhook()
    API -> DB: Find PaymentTransaction\nby orderCode
    DB --> API: PaymentTransaction\n(purpose=OVERDUE_PAYMENT)
    API -> API: Set transaction.status = PAID
    API -> API: Check all pending payments resolved
    API -> API: Set booking.status = COMPLETED
    API -> DB: save(transaction + booking)
    DB --> API: Saved

    == Step 7: Booking Complete ==

    Staff -> FE: Refresh booking detail
    FE -> API: GET /api/staff/bookings/{bookingId}
    API --> FE: AdminBookingResponse\n(status=COMPLETED)
    FE --> Staff: Show "Booking Complete" banner\n(no further actions)
end

@enduml
